partnerDetails.about:
At Simpson Electrical Ltd we make sure you get the best job done, every time, and we will come up with inventive solutions to make your dream a reality.

With over 18 years experience in the electrical industry working in all fields, from small one off residential jobs, to light commercial jobs start to finish, to the planning, design and completion of all electrical work in your new home build, we are sure to come up with a plan that suits!

As a registered member of the Master Electricians Association of New Zealand all our workmanship is guaranteed.
